snippet.title: The Cope | Ghost of The SEA 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the shoes of a night janitor, shrouded in secrets and danger.

The Cope is a Survival Horror Point and Click game. Your night shift guest service job as a janitor will start with you getting entangled in a series of strange stories in The Cope mansion, with unknown rules and fear.

Twitter : x.com/TheCopeGame
Steam : store.steampowered.com/app/2979860/THE_COPE/
